title: FBoy Island,’ ‘Love Island UK,’ ‘The Challenge,’ ‘Real Housewives of Beverly Hills,’ and ‘Sweet Life: Los Angeles’ | Reality Top 5
description:
1. Callie and Juliet debate the merits and pitfalls of the “F-boy”–“nice guy” dichotomy on ‘FBoy Island’ (0:30).
2. Juliet shares her impressions of ‘Love Island UK’ Season 7 after watching her first episodes ever (11:53).
3. Juliet and Callie discuss their favorite and least favorite vets on this season of ‘The Challenge’ and the vets vs. rookies dynamic (22:50).
4. It’s all about Erika on ‘Real Housewives of Beverly Hills.’ How could her lawyers let her go on the show? How could she not read the papers her husband had asked her to sign? We ponder those questions and more (36:27).
5. Juliet tells Callie about a new show on HBO Max from producer Issa Rae called ‘Sweet Life: Los Angeles,’ which is basically ‘Insecure’ in real life (53:30).
Hosts: Juliet Litman and Callie Curry
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
